verbose_text: These viruses, as well as pseudotype retroviruses (HCVpp) or HCVcc, were sensitive to the inhibitors of vacuolar acidification, such as ammonium chloride, concanamycin A, or bafilomycin A 1, or formation of clathrin coated pits, chlorpromazine, suggesting that these viruses enter via pH dependent and clathrin mediated endocytosis into target cells.
